WEBVTT

00:00:16.934 --> 00:00:20.521
Huh? Okay, where am I?

00:00:20.562 --> 00:00:24.066
Ooh! Maybe it's a
haunted house? Cool!

00:00:24.107 --> 00:00:28.987
[MAYU laughs] Where are you,
ghosts? Come out and play!

00:00:29.029 --> 00:00:30.989
Ghosts, ghosts, ghosts!

00:00:31.031 --> 00:00:34.409
You're here to stay,
so come out and play!

00:00:36.703 --> 00:00:38.080
Huh?

00:00:40.249 --> 00:00:40.916
[GINTI]
Hey.

00:00:40.958 --> 00:00:42.918
[gasps] You talking to me?

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:45.921
You see anybody
else around here?

00:00:45.963 --> 00:00:48.257
Just sit over there.

00:00:48.298 --> 00:00:50.759
Since you asked nicely.

00:02:13.133 --> 00:02:16.928
[footsteps, rustling]

00:02:16.970 --> 00:02:18.513
Are you a collector?

00:02:18.555 --> 00:02:19.139
Don't touch those!

00:02:19.181 --> 00:02:20.474
[grunts]

00:02:21.850 --> 00:02:23.685
Took your sweet
time gettin' here.

00:02:23.727 --> 00:02:25.979
I'm gonna make the
spiel quick, so listen up.

00:02:26.021 --> 00:02:27.105
You ready?

00:02:27.147 --> 00:02:28.398
[MAYU]
What spiel?

00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:29.941
In a bit, I'm gonna
have you play a game

00:02:29.983 --> 00:02:31.568
against that dude over there.

00:02:31.610 --> 00:02:33.362
[MAYU]
What do you mean "play a game"?

00:02:33.403 --> 00:02:37.240
What's going on? I don't get
the point of this. Do you?

00:02:37.282 --> 00:02:39.451
[MAYU gasps]

00:02:39.493 --> 00:02:41.453
[MAYU]
No way.

00:02:41.495 --> 00:02:42.329
Hey, um.

00:02:42.371 --> 00:02:45.290
I could be totally wrong
about this, but you look like

00:02:45.332 --> 00:02:48.126
Harada from Cross Heart Attack.

00:02:48.168 --> 00:02:49.044
Guilty.

00:02:49.086 --> 00:02:52.673
[MAYU]
No! Freaking! Way!

00:02:52.714 --> 00:02:55.550
[MAYU giggles]
I am your biggest fan!

00:02:55.592 --> 00:02:58.261
I don't know what I'm doing
here, but I don't care!

00:02:58.303 --> 00:02:59.888
Oh, nice to meet you, too.

00:02:59.930 --> 00:03:02.099
I would be so honored
if you'd shake my hand!

00:03:02.140 --> 00:03:03.642
I'm Mayu Arita.

00:03:03.684 --> 00:03:04.643
Sure. No problem.

00:03:04.685 --> 00:03:07.813
[MAYU squeals]

00:03:07.854 --> 00:03:10.107
[HARADA]
What is that?

00:03:10.148 --> 00:03:11.775
And you're the one who
brought us together!

00:03:11.817 --> 00:03:15.529
Thank you! Uh, so,
who are you, anyway?

00:03:15.570 --> 00:03:16.780
Name's Ginti.

00:03:16.822 --> 00:03:19.116
[MAYU] Huh? That's
kind of a weird name.

00:03:19.157 --> 00:03:21.159
Are you C. H. A.'s
manager or something?

00:03:21.201 --> 00:03:23.870
[GINTI]
This is gonna be a long shift.

00:03:23.912 --> 00:03:25.831
[GINTI]
Listen, just press this.

00:03:25.872 --> 00:03:27.958
That'll pick what game you play.

00:03:29.084 --> 00:03:30.544
Playing a game with Harada?

00:03:30.585 --> 00:03:33.505
I'm so totally in! Oh, do you
mind if I press the button?

00:03:33.547 --> 00:03:35.006
Well, apparently we
can't leave here

00:03:35.048 --> 00:03:37.217
till we play this
game. So, go ahead.

00:03:37.259 --> 00:03:38.593
Here we go!

00:03:40.303 --> 00:03:45.642
[MAYU gasps]
Ooh...

00:03:45.684 --> 00:03:47.644
[game music plays]

00:03:49.396 --> 00:03:52.023
Um, so, what's that?

00:03:52.065 --> 00:03:53.567
Never heard of it.

00:03:53.608 --> 00:03:55.777
All right, follow me.

00:03:58.655 --> 00:04:00.741
Aw, what a cute little kitty!

00:04:00.782 --> 00:04:01.825
[HARADA]
You comin'?

00:04:01.867 --> 00:04:03.201
Oh! Yeah!

00:04:04.786 --> 00:04:07.539
[MAYU] I wonder what this
place is. Do you know?

00:04:07.581 --> 00:04:08.999
[HARADA]
No clue.

00:04:13.837 --> 00:04:16.089
[MAYU]
So, no shows today, huh?

00:04:16.131 --> 00:04:19.384
[HARADA] Nope. I guess
it must be my day off.

00:04:19.426 --> 00:04:21.720
Only, I can't seem to
remember how I got here.

00:04:21.762 --> 00:04:22.637
What about you?

00:04:22.679 --> 00:04:23.847
No, I got nothin'!

00:04:23.889 --> 00:04:25.932
Looks like you're
taking it pretty well.

00:04:25.974 --> 00:04:27.350
[MAYU]
I'm here, chatting with Harada.

00:04:27.392 --> 00:04:29.227
Nothing's gonna
ruin that for me.

00:04:29.269 --> 00:04:30.937
[HARADA]
Right...

00:04:30.979 --> 00:04:34.733
Ooh! That's huge!

00:04:44.534 --> 00:04:46.703
[GINTI grunts]

00:04:46.745 --> 00:04:48.663
[MAYU] I've got no idea
how to play this.

00:04:48.705 --> 00:04:51.416
Well, gimme a sec. I'll explain.

00:04:51.458 --> 00:04:53.084
Take your socks off
and stand on the edge.

00:04:53.126 --> 00:04:54.795
All right.

00:04:57.672 --> 00:05:00.091
The spinner is gonna
give you your instructions.

00:05:00.133 --> 00:05:01.593
[MAYU]
What spinner?

00:05:01.635 --> 00:05:04.638
This thing up here. It spins.

00:05:08.517 --> 00:05:10.977
[MAYU] The kitty's the
one who controls it?

00:05:11.019 --> 00:05:14.105
[GINTI]
Memine! Call her by her name.

00:05:14.147 --> 00:05:14.856
[MAYU]
Okay.

00:05:14.898 --> 00:05:17.025
Now, back to the instructions.

00:05:17.067 --> 00:05:19.069
Just do what the
spinner tells you to.

00:05:19.110 --> 00:05:22.781
Place the selected body part
on the selected circle.

00:05:22.823 --> 00:05:24.866
If you fall or if you
touch the mat beyond

00:05:24.908 --> 00:05:28.495
what's specified,
then, you lose.

00:05:28.537 --> 00:05:30.080
That's it, those are the rules.

00:05:30.121 --> 00:05:31.498
Everybody got it?

00:05:31.540 --> 00:05:33.750
Yeah, that sounds
simple enough to me.

00:05:33.792 --> 00:05:35.544
[game dings]

00:05:39.548 --> 00:05:42.884
[SPINNER VOICE]
Player one, left hand to blue.

00:05:42.926 --> 00:05:44.678
[GINTI]
Ladies first, I guess.

00:05:44.719 --> 00:05:46.555
You mean we're
starting already?

00:05:46.596 --> 00:05:47.681
That's the idea.

00:05:47.722 --> 00:05:49.599
[MAYU] You're really
grouchy, you know that?

00:05:49.641 --> 00:05:51.142
And my name's Mayu, by the way.

00:05:51.184 --> 00:05:52.519
You could try using it.

00:05:52.561 --> 00:05:54.604
Don't really care what
your name is, honey.

00:05:54.646 --> 00:05:56.481
--Just start playing.
--[MAYU] Ugh!

00:05:56.523 --> 00:05:59.568
[MAYU] What is this guy's
problem? He's a real ass.

00:05:59.609 --> 00:06:01.069
[gasps]

00:06:01.111 --> 00:06:05.156
[MAYU] Good, he wasn't
watching. Calm down, Mayu!

00:06:05.198 --> 00:06:06.741
[game dings]

00:06:11.746 --> 00:06:15.834
[SPINNER VOICE] Player two,
right foot to yellow.

00:06:15.876 --> 00:06:17.586
[game dings]

00:06:20.797 --> 00:06:23.008
[SPINNER VOICE] Player one,
right hand to blue.

00:06:23.049 --> 00:06:26.052
You get the idea.
Have a grand old time.

00:06:26.094 --> 00:06:27.178
Sounds easy enough.

00:06:27.220 --> 00:06:28.680
[game dings]

00:06:29.681 --> 00:06:32.893
Player two, left hand to blue.

00:06:32.934 --> 00:06:34.060
Aw, yeah!

00:06:34.102 --> 00:06:35.228
[gasps]

00:06:36.730 --> 00:06:38.273
Uh...

00:06:42.444 --> 00:06:45.614
[MAYU humming]

00:06:49.284 --> 00:06:51.578
[MAYU] I guess you can't
expect a guy not to look.

00:06:51.620 --> 00:06:54.956
And considering who it is, it's
not like I'm gonna complain!

00:06:54.998 --> 00:06:57.083
Is there something wrong, Mayu?
It's your turn to move.

00:06:57.125 --> 00:07:00.337
[MAYU] Gah! He said it!
He said my name!

00:07:00.378 --> 00:07:02.923
I can officially die happy now!

00:07:04.299 --> 00:07:07.218
[SPINNER VOICE]
Player two, right hand to red.

00:07:07.260 --> 00:07:08.261
[game dings]

00:07:08.303 --> 00:07:11.222
[HARADA sighs] I guess
I have to play this game,

00:07:11.264 --> 00:07:12.891
but I wish the girl
was a little cuter.

00:07:12.933 --> 00:07:15.518
[SPINNER VOICE] Player one,
right hand to yellow.

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:17.354
[HARADA]
She's just too obvious.

00:07:17.395 --> 00:07:18.772
[laughs]

00:07:18.813 --> 00:07:19.230
[laughs]

00:07:19.272 --> 00:07:22.150
[HARADA] I just wanna get out
of here so I can see Lisa.

00:07:24.653 --> 00:07:27.072
[door clicks]

00:07:40.043 --> 00:07:43.213
[SPINNER VOICE]
Player one, right foot to blue.

00:07:44.339 --> 00:07:47.092
[MAYU grunts]

00:07:47.133 --> 00:07:49.177
Whew! Almost fell!

00:07:49.219 --> 00:07:53.264
[SPINNER VOICE]
Player two, left foot to yellow.

00:07:53.306 --> 00:07:56.101
Left foot to yellow.
How's that gonna work?

00:07:58.687 --> 00:08:00.605
[HARADA]
Hm.

00:08:00.647 --> 00:08:01.815
[HARADA grunts]

00:08:03.191 --> 00:08:04.859
[gasps]

00:08:06.027 --> 00:08:07.195
--[HARADA grunts]
--[game dings]

00:08:07.237 --> 00:08:08.279
Amazing!

00:08:08.321 --> 00:08:11.282
No wonder they call you
C. H. A.'s dance prince!

00:08:11.324 --> 00:08:12.450
--[SPINNER VOICE] Player one,
--It was nothing.

00:08:12.492 --> 00:08:14.285
--left hand to red.
--It was nothing.

00:08:14.327 --> 00:08:17.539
[MAYU]
Oh! He is just too cool!

00:08:17.580 --> 00:08:20.709
And I'm close enough to
smell his sweat! Yummy!

00:08:28.008 --> 00:08:29.801
[yawns]

00:08:33.805 --> 00:08:37.183
[MAYU giggles]

00:08:38.893 --> 00:08:43.273
[MAYU] Ah! This is bliss!
If only I could stop time!

00:08:43.314 --> 00:08:46.276
I wish this game could
go on forever and ever!

00:08:48.945 --> 00:08:53.616
Okay. I'm getting tired.
My arms can't take much more.

00:08:53.658 --> 00:08:56.161
[MAYU]
And I have to pee.

00:08:56.202 --> 00:08:58.788
[MAYU]
Hey. Can you hear me?

00:08:58.830 --> 00:09:00.457
Yeah? What do you want?

00:09:00.498 --> 00:09:02.000
I need to take a little break.

00:09:02.042 --> 00:09:02.709
[GINTI]
Why's that?

00:09:02.751 --> 00:09:05.420
[MAYU growls]
You get one, so why can't we?

00:09:05.462 --> 00:09:08.381
I'm tired, okay? And I
need to use the restroom.

00:09:08.423 --> 00:09:09.382
Too bad.

00:09:09.424 --> 00:09:11.509
Come on! What is your problem?

00:09:11.551 --> 00:09:14.095
It isn't just me. Harada
wants a break, too.

00:09:14.137 --> 00:09:15.472
I could use one.

00:09:15.513 --> 00:09:17.682
It's not gonna happen,
so quit bothering me.

00:09:17.724 --> 00:09:19.642
And there's one more
thing I forgot to say.

00:09:19.684 --> 00:09:22.896
There'll be consequences
for the loser.

00:09:22.937 --> 00:09:25.857
Potentially fatal consequences.

00:09:25.899 --> 00:09:27.817
Is that supposed to be
a joke or something?

00:09:27.859 --> 00:09:29.736
'Cause it's not very funny.

00:09:29.778 --> 00:09:34.157
[GINTI] A cruel joke, I guess
you could call it. See this?

00:09:34.199 --> 00:09:35.784
What is it?

00:09:35.825 --> 00:09:37.619
You think I'm just
kidding around?

00:09:37.660 --> 00:09:39.662
Let me prove I'm serious.

00:09:45.794 --> 00:09:47.170
What?

00:09:47.212 --> 00:09:48.254
[gasps]

00:09:48.296 --> 00:09:50.673
[cackling]

00:09:50.715 --> 00:09:52.550
Ew, creepy!

00:10:02.977 --> 00:10:06.064
[MAYU] That's it! What the
hell is going on here?

00:10:06.106 --> 00:10:08.483
This is the beginning
of the actual game.

00:10:08.525 --> 00:10:11.194
Hope you two kids
have a lovely time.

00:10:21.704 --> 00:10:23.540
Well, what are
you waiting for?

00:10:23.581 --> 00:10:26.334
It says left hand, red.
Let's get to it.

00:10:26.376 --> 00:10:27.919
Fine!

00:10:32.257 --> 00:10:33.424
What?

00:10:33.466 --> 00:10:34.926
What happened?

00:10:34.968 --> 00:10:36.219
[BOTH gasp]

00:10:36.261 --> 00:10:38.263
Hot!

00:10:38.304 --> 00:10:39.848
This is a prank, right?

00:10:39.889 --> 00:10:42.016
It burns! Ow!

00:10:42.058 --> 00:10:43.726
You can stop it now!

00:10:43.768 --> 00:10:45.353
[MAYU]
Come on! Turn it off!

00:10:45.395 --> 00:10:46.980
[GINTI] This is the most
fun I've had all day.

00:10:47.021 --> 00:10:48.314
Why would I stop it?

00:10:48.356 --> 00:10:51.067
I can't wait to see who's
gonna lose their balance first.

00:10:51.109 --> 00:10:53.653
--[MAYU groaning]
--Hot! Hot!

00:10:56.030 --> 00:10:58.658
[MAYU]
Quick! It's left hand green!

00:11:02.996 --> 00:11:05.039
[HARADA gasps]

00:11:05.081 --> 00:11:07.292
[yelps]

00:11:07.333 --> 00:11:09.210
That feels nice!

00:11:09.252 --> 00:11:10.211
Huh?

00:11:10.253 --> 00:11:12.172
[screams]

00:11:13.673 --> 00:11:14.924
You can just turn around!

00:11:14.966 --> 00:11:16.593
[GINTI] You really think
anybody's interested

00:11:16.634 --> 00:11:18.595
in whatever you've
got under there?

00:11:18.636 --> 00:11:20.930
[growls] What did you say to me?

00:11:20.972 --> 00:11:25.185
[screaming]

00:11:25.226 --> 00:11:29.230
[MAYU] This wind's too strong.
I can't take a breath.

00:11:29.272 --> 00:11:31.941
Quick! It's your move!

00:11:31.983 --> 00:11:34.444
[MAYU]
Oh, right. Blue.

00:11:41.409 --> 00:11:44.078
Well, player two, move your
right foot to yellow.

00:11:44.120 --> 00:11:48.166
[BOTH panting]

00:11:48.208 --> 00:11:49.584
You should really
focus on the game,

00:11:49.626 --> 00:11:51.044
unless you wanna die.

00:11:51.085 --> 00:11:58.801
[panting]

00:11:58.843 --> 00:12:00.970
Freezing!

00:12:01.012 --> 00:12:03.765
Right foot yellow.
That's not good.

00:12:05.058 --> 00:12:06.684
[HARADA]
It'll be close.

00:12:06.726 --> 00:12:09.854
D-D-Do you think
you can do it?

00:12:11.564 --> 00:12:13.775
[gasps]

00:12:13.816 --> 00:12:17.195
[HARADA] It's frozen?
No way! That isn't fair!

00:12:17.237 --> 00:12:18.613
That's the kinda
thing that happens

00:12:18.655 --> 00:12:20.031
when you dilly-dally.

00:12:20.073 --> 00:12:23.910
[HARADA grunting]

00:12:23.952 --> 00:12:25.370
Damn it!

00:12:25.411 --> 00:12:28.539
[panting]

00:12:28.581 --> 00:12:31.542
[MAYU] This is it.
We're gonna die here.

00:12:31.584 --> 00:12:35.129
Although, this could
be a "Titanic" moment!

00:12:35.171 --> 00:12:37.632
Wouldn't that be romantic?

00:12:37.674 --> 00:12:39.717
These poses are
kinda awkward, though.

00:12:39.759 --> 00:12:42.220
[grunting]

00:12:48.017 --> 00:12:51.646
--[panting]
--[crackling]

00:12:51.688 --> 00:12:57.652
[HARADA grunting]

00:12:57.694 --> 00:13:00.071
Can he do it?

00:13:00.113 --> 00:13:04.993
You should never doubt
the dance prince!

00:13:06.536 --> 00:13:09.706
[HARADA yells]

00:13:18.506 --> 00:13:24.929
[FANGIRLS chanting]
C. H. A.! C. H. A.! C. H. A.! C. H. A.!

00:13:24.971 --> 00:13:26.514
[MAYU]
Harada...

00:13:29.309 --> 00:13:31.144
[MAYU]
Harada!

00:13:32.145 --> 00:13:34.605
[GIRLS cheer]

00:13:34.647 --> 00:13:36.941
[laughs]

00:13:45.575 --> 00:13:48.286
I can't believe we did it!
You were amazing!

00:13:48.328 --> 00:13:49.829
I thought we were gonna die!

00:13:49.871 --> 00:13:53.833
[panting] It was nothin'!

00:13:59.672 --> 00:14:01.799
--Huh? What now?
--[HARADA] Not again!

00:14:04.177 --> 00:14:05.553
[gasps]

00:14:05.595 --> 00:14:07.555
[MAYU]
Oh, god! No way!

00:14:07.597 --> 00:14:10.433
[HARADA, MAYU scream]

00:14:10.475 --> 00:14:11.893
Stunning view, isn't it?

00:14:11.934 --> 00:14:14.437
You psycho! Get us out of here!

00:14:14.479 --> 00:14:16.189
[GINTI]
No, I don't think I will.

00:14:16.230 --> 00:14:17.273
This may come as a surprise,

00:14:17.315 --> 00:14:19.609
but I don't actually care
what happens to you.

00:14:19.650 --> 00:14:23.654
This is my favorite part
of the whole thing.

00:14:23.696 --> 00:14:26.115
Welcome to the
sudden death round.

00:14:26.157 --> 00:14:30.203
The game's about to end. Just as
soon as one of you falls.

00:14:31.829 --> 00:14:34.123
[GINTI] There. Took a while,
but we've finally

00:14:34.165 --> 00:14:38.586
reached the entertaining
part. Pathetic humans.

00:14:38.628 --> 00:14:41.089
[HARADA]
When one of us... falls?

00:14:42.298 --> 00:14:44.634
[MAYU]
Oh, god.

00:14:44.675 --> 00:14:49.222
[HARADA]
Falls or... gets pushed.

00:14:49.263 --> 00:14:50.848
[MAYU]
What do I do?

00:14:50.890 --> 00:14:53.976
[panting]

00:14:55.770 --> 00:14:58.106
[MAYU]
I can't.

00:14:58.147 --> 00:15:03.861
[HARADA whimpering]

00:15:03.903 --> 00:15:06.197
[HARADA]
It's either her or me.

00:15:09.700 --> 00:15:15.957
[MAYU] It's... hopeless.
I can't hold it anymore!

00:15:17.542 --> 00:15:20.378
[MAYU] I can't pee myself
in front of Harada.

00:15:20.420 --> 00:15:22.171
I'd rather...

00:15:25.007 --> 00:15:27.343
[MAYU]
It's over. I quit.

00:15:30.012 --> 00:15:31.889
It's been amazing.

00:15:31.931 --> 00:15:34.517
I got to play a game,
one-on-one, with Harada.

00:15:34.559 --> 00:15:37.061
What more could a girl ask for?

00:15:37.103 --> 00:15:41.149
I'm so happy. This is
a dream come true.

00:15:41.190 --> 00:15:45.570
Ever since that first concert,
I've been your biggest fan.

00:15:45.611 --> 00:15:48.156
I went to your shows
and bought your posters.

00:15:48.197 --> 00:15:53.202
I even sent you fan mail.
A lot of fan mail.

00:15:53.244 --> 00:15:56.956
Whenever things got tough,
or I was having a bad day,

00:15:56.998 --> 00:16:00.877
I would listen to your songs,
and they would cheer me up.

00:16:02.879 --> 00:16:06.716
Well, anyway. I guess what
I'm saying is, thanks.

00:16:06.757 --> 00:16:09.927
Thanks, Harada, for
always being there.

00:16:11.345 --> 00:16:13.598
[MAYU]
