00:16:45.755 --> 00:16:47.757
[laughs]

00:16:52.678 --> 00:16:58.809
[HARADA] Kana, oh my god.
I didn't want this to happen.

00:16:58.851 --> 00:17:02.980
No, my fans deserve better.

00:17:03.022 --> 00:17:05.399
If I can ask one thing,
please don't forget me.

00:17:05.441 --> 00:17:08.236
Good luck with C. H. A. and your
dancing and everything.

00:17:08.277 --> 00:17:09.862
You'll be great!

00:17:12.240 --> 00:17:13.241
Well, goodbye.

00:17:13.282 --> 00:17:14.617
[HARADA gasps]

00:17:19.372 --> 00:17:22.625
[HARADA]
No! Not this again!

00:17:25.002 --> 00:17:27.505
What are you doing?

00:17:27.547 --> 00:17:29.423
[HARADA]
I can't let you do this.

00:17:29.465 --> 00:17:33.719
We'll find some way
out. Right, Mayu?

00:17:33.761 --> 00:17:35.763
Without you, I'd be nothing!

00:17:35.805 --> 00:17:37.723
Huh?

00:17:37.765 --> 00:17:39.850
[HARADA]
My fans make me who I am.

00:17:39.892 --> 00:17:41.769
They make me a success!

00:17:41.811 --> 00:17:44.730
It's because of them that
I've come so far in my life.

00:17:44.772 --> 00:17:47.024
It's because of you, Mayu!

00:17:47.066 --> 00:17:49.735
How could I forget
something as basic as that?

00:17:49.777 --> 00:17:51.821
It won't happen again!

00:17:51.862 --> 00:17:54.824
[MAYU] You... You really
mean that! Wow.

00:17:56.450 --> 00:17:58.661
[grunts]

00:18:00.705 --> 00:18:04.792
I can't let it end like this.
I can't do it! Promise me!

00:18:04.834 --> 00:18:07.420
Say you'll come to one
of my concerts again!

00:18:07.461 --> 00:18:09.171
Yeah!

00:18:09.213 --> 00:18:12.341
[HARADA] Do you promise?
I want you to promise!

00:18:12.383 --> 00:18:16.220
[MAYU]
Yes! I promise you I will!

00:18:16.262 --> 00:18:19.181
Thank you for that.

00:18:19.223 --> 00:18:20.683
Sure.

00:18:26.439 --> 00:18:31.027
No!

00:18:32.820 --> 00:18:34.030
[gasps]

00:18:34.071 --> 00:18:36.324
[MAYU]
What an awesome show!

00:18:36.365 --> 00:18:42.330
Harada was so amazing!
C. H. A.! C. H. A.! C--

00:18:42.371 --> 00:18:44.081
H--

00:18:46.834 --> 00:18:49.170
No way!

00:18:50.338 --> 00:18:53.049
[screams]

00:18:57.845 --> 00:18:59.013
Huh?

00:19:01.140 --> 00:19:03.267
Huh?!

00:19:03.309 --> 00:19:07.563
[HARADA] Damn it. Damn it!
How could this happen?

00:19:07.605 --> 00:19:10.650
Another woman gone
because of me!

00:19:11.901 --> 00:19:14.362
[LISA]
Wake up, Harada.

00:19:14.403 --> 00:19:16.614
Are you awake?

00:19:16.656 --> 00:19:20.409
I wanted to let you know
I'm leaving. Goodbye.

00:19:20.451 --> 00:19:22.411
It's early. You have
to leave already?

00:19:22.453 --> 00:19:24.121
[door clicks]

00:19:30.252 --> 00:19:36.717
[ticking]

00:19:36.759 --> 00:19:38.636
--[yells]
