[MAYU]
Oh, just shut it!

00:19:54.652 --> 00:19:55.403
'Scuse me?

00:19:55.444 --> 00:19:57.822
[MAYU growling]
Alive or dead, whatever,

00:19:57.863 --> 00:19:59.573
I just need a change of clothes!

00:19:59.615 --> 00:20:03.285
I couldn't hold it anymore!
I need a shower!

00:20:03.327 --> 00:20:05.037
Well, this is interesting.

00:20:05.079 --> 00:20:08.082
You heard the part about
being dead, right?

00:20:08.124 --> 00:20:10.084
