[GINTI]
I said, don't touch it!

00:20:29.562 --> 00:20:31.230
Sorry for the delay.

00:20:33.232 --> 00:20:34.775
[MAYU]
Hm?

00:20:37.611 --> 00:20:38.571
Who the hell are you?

00:20:38.612 --> 00:20:42.074
[MAYU] Ugh! I told you!
My name is Mayu!

00:20:42.116 --> 00:20:44.869
[GINTI]
Ah! Moron! What did you do?

00:20:44.910 --> 00:20:45.494
Pick it up!

00:20:45.536 --> 00:20:46.996
Wow, I didn't
recognize you at all!

00:20:47.037 --> 00:20:47.747
Huh?

00:20:47.788 --> 00:20:49.498
You look a whole lot
cuter this way.

00:20:49.540 --> 00:20:50.958
Really? I do?

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:53.335
Yeah, you're totally my type!

00:20:53.377 --> 00:20:55.921
Whoa-ho-ho-ho!

00:20:55.963 --> 00:20:57.173
[GINTI grunting]

00:20:57.214 --> 00:20:57.840
[MAYU]
You mean it?

00:20:57.882 --> 00:20:58.799
--[HARADA] Yeah!
--[MAYU] Oh!

00:20:58.841 --> 00:21:00.843
